{"word":"ἀνάπαυμα","slug":"ἀνάπαυμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάπαυμα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναπαύω'><el>ἀναπαύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a repose, rest</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>; <el>μεριμνῶν</el> from cares, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a resting-place</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}